# Copy to `.npmrc` in this package's root for LOCAL publishing only
# (CI uses the workflow's built-in GITHUB_TOKEN instead — you don't need
# this file for the GitHub Actions publish path).
#
# 1. Create a GitHub personal access token (classic) with the
#    `write:packages` scope: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# 2. Replace mbsatimov below with your GitHub org/username.
# 3. Export the token before publishing:
#      export NPM_TOKEN=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxx
#      npm publish

//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${NPM_TOKEN}
@mbsatimov:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
